Tropical Weather Outlook
NWS Central Pacific Hurricane Center Honolulu HI
200 PM HST Tue Nov 26 2024

For the central North Pacific...between 140W and 180W:

No tropical cyclones are expected during the next 7 days.

The central North Pacific hurricane season officially ends on
November 30. The final Tropical Weather Outlook of the season will
be issued at 8 PM HST on November 30. Routine issuance of the
Tropical Weather Outlook will resume on June 1, 2025. During the
off-season, Special Tropical Weather Outlooks will be issued as
conditions warrant.

$$
Forecaster Almanza
